{"tid":762031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【貿易開戰】美商務部長羅斯：現在是強硬對待中國的好時機","createTime":"2018-07-31T02:26:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T04:47:32.000Z","uid":79563,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"65e5aed842603d2538f7fe9d29fa01b1252e2621","tid":762031,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T02:26:07.000Z","msg":"《經濟通通訊社３１日專訊》美國商務部長羅斯在論壇上發言時表示，美國近期經濟表現強勁，可以吸收和中國貿易衝突所產生的短期痛苦，現在是對華持強硬立場的好時機。但羅斯又認為，目前局面持續下去，不符合各方利益，相信最終美國將通過談判與中國達成解決方案，為美國企業帶來成果。<br />\n<br />\n　　羅斯又提到，美國尋求在印度洋－太平洋地區訂立一系列雙邊貿易協定。（ｅｙ）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=editorchoice&amp;newsid=ETN280731838\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fwww%2Ftc%2Fnews%2Fcategorized_news_detail.php%3Fcategory%3Deditorchoice%26newsid%3DETN280731838&d=ZwXxiz8aJHjnUpSvs3T%2F7i7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=12ef9b1e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=editorchoice&amp;newsid=ETN280731838</a>"},{"pid":"839c73cdb14285dcc723fe689522863a816448a1","tid":762031,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T02:27:09.000Z","msg":"留名等五毛入黎講中國好，香港才會好"},{"pid":"1c1a6a9f0e64d4e6b759e1b1d9ab367e5eae6826","tid":762031,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"839c73cdb14285dcc723fe689522863a816448a1","tid":762031,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T02:27:09.000Z","msg":"留名等五毛入黎講中國好，香港才會好"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T02:34:01.000Z","msg":"或者支那衰，香港仲衰"},{"pid":"7b7ce8d967f8105abc161e4f2458daf4e7ca1cd9","tid":762031,"uid":23833,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1c1a6a9f0e64d4e6b759e1b1d9ab367e5eae6826","tid":762031,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"839c73cdb14285dcc723fe689522863a816448a1","tid":762031,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T02:27: